    • Method Detail

      • onDeleteDone

        void onDeleteDone​(Integer token,
                  Object cookie,
                  Integer result)
        Called to process the data deletion result.

        This method is called after data is deleted from the database.

        Parameters:
        token - Indicates the token. It must be consistent with that in the DataAbilityAsyncHandler#addDeleteJob or RdbStoreAsyncHandler#addDeleteJob method.
        cookie - Indicates the cookie. It can be null.
        result - Indicates the data deletion result. If it is null, an exception occurs during the data deletion.
        Since:
        3
